                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9786" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1477</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">861 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风控迷局数字破，新航早借技术风 ——M商业银行信贷风险管理优化之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Resolve Credit Risk Challenges Digitally, Start New Optimization Early with Tech— The Optimization Path of M Commercial Bank&#39;s Credit Risk Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李永红，王梁，赵佳瑶，宋凯，牛亚琳，赵亚楠，赵婧洋，宋昊骏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国民生银行股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安全监察部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">商业银行；信贷业务；风险管理；数字化技术</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Commercial Banks; Credit business; Risk management; Digital technology</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例聚焦 M 商业银行的发展轨迹，深入探讨其公司信贷业务风险管理变革，旨在为金融专业学生提供宝贵的实践洞察与学习素材。M 商业银行自成立后规模迅速扩张，但信贷业务问题渐显，不良贷款率攀升、客户结构劣化。案例详述其信贷业务各阶段状况，如初创奠基期的良好开局、快速发展期的风险累积等。针对贷前调查新技术运用不足、贷中审查流程繁琐、贷后风险预警滞后等问题，银行采取系列数字化优化措施，包括构建客户信息识别与推送系统、建立数字化放款分层审批机制、打造贷后智能风险预警监测平台等。通过这些举措，不良贷款率下降，客户结构优化。学生可借此案例学习如何剖析银行信贷风险问题根源，理解数字化技术在风险管理各环节的应用原理与优势，掌握优化风险管理流程的策略与方法，提升金融风险识别、分析与应对能力，为未来从事金融行业工作奠定坚实基础，培养在复杂金融环境中运用创新手段解决实际问题的专业素养。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study focuses on the development trajectory of M Commercial Bank and explores the risk management reform of its corporate credit business, aiming to provide valuable practical insights and learning materials for finance students. Since its establishment, M Commercial Bank has expanded rapidly, but its credit business problems have gradually emerged, with the non-performing loan ratio rising and the customer structure deteriorating. The case details the status of each stage of its credit business, such as the good start of the start-up foundation period and the accumulation of risks in the rapid development period. In response to problems such as the insufficient use of new technologies for pre-loan investigation, the cumbersome review process during loans, and the lag in post-loan risk early warning, banks have adopted a series of digital optimization measures, including building a customer information identification and push system, establishing a digital lending hierarchical approval mechanism, and building a post-loan intelligent risk early warning and monitoring platform. Through these measures, the non-performing loan ratio has been reduced and the customer structure has been optimized. Students can use this case study to learn how to analyze the root cause of bank credit risk problems, understand the application principles and advantages of digital technology in all aspects of risk management, master the strategies and methods to optimize the risk management process, improve the ability to identify, analyze and respond to financial risks, lay a solid foundation for future work in the financial industry, and cultivate professional quality to use innovative means to solve practical problems in a complex financial environment.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司战略与风险管理》、《内部控制与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司信贷业务风险管理；内部控制理论；企业风险管理整合框架；数字金融；金融科技；AIGC技术</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
